{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_01","textHome":"我家作为代代相传的「华心流」本家，是从@江户时期延续下来的花道一门。父亲重传统，@追求彻底的古代技法，处处流露出@精雕细琢的美丽……强烈地吸引着我的心，@所以我也很自然地跟着父亲学习花道。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_18","textHome":"要取胜就不能错失「良机」，这是铁则。@只是说起来容易，做起来难啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_19","textHome":"似乎跨越了阻碍……那就继续前进吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_20","textHome":"直觉变得意外地敏锐，但内心却很平静……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_21","textHome":"以前除了花道，我还学过很多东西。我想想，@香道、三味线长歌、茶道、嘻哈舞……@最后那个是开玩笑啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_22","textHome":"我也学过拔刀术哦。中学二年级时还被授予了@初段称号。心无杂念，单单拔出刀剑……@这个动作，就和父亲插花的姿态一样。@我想其中也有什么共通之处吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_23","textHome":"我学拔刀术时，参观过龙真馆的剑道场演武，@那时我才刚来神滨。说来，还有个挥舞着长刀@和我年龄相仿的女孩子。真是让人怀念呀。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_24","textHome":"贵安。很高兴能与你再次相见。@再次与我结伴同行如何？@那么，走吧……前往我们的战场。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_25","textHome":"睡醒了吗？早安。出门前一起散散步怎么样？@适当运动一下，最能让心情舒畅了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_26","textHome":"啊，都这个时间了。那该去吃午饭了……@今天……就去小卖部吃荞麦面如何？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_27","textHome":"以前的黄昏时刻，也被称为逢魔之时。@也就是，会遇到魔物的时间带……@总感觉能听到魔女蠢蠢欲动的声音……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_03","textHome":"「宿命」……我将会背负它。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_28","textHome":"夜已深了。睡前看会儿书，然后顺着睡意就寝@……这是我的习惯呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_29","textHome":"时间是不管你愿意与否都会径直流逝的东西。@直到记忆远去，自己也一并消失……@哎，人的一生竟如此虚幻……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_30","textHome":"我不会逃避自己的命运……@我会面对它，然后尽力改变。@我的人生，是由我自己决定的……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_31","textHome":"是比试吗？我明白了……那就来比试一场吧。@不过，我是不会手下留情的。还请了解……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_32","textHome":"战斗的形势变得极其混乱啊。@越是这种时候，越要占据制高点纵观全局。@一起寻找可乘之机吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_33","textHome":"只用一朵花和一片叶的插花叫「一花一叶」。@去除多余的东西，留下纯粹的美……@但愿人生也能如此。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_34","textHome":"我喜欢什么花？嗯……喜欢的有很多，@其中之一就是鸢尾花了。@虽然很难养活，但却会让我心动。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_35","textHome":"在店门口之类的地方看见有趣的容器的话，@我就忍不住会想，怎么用它来插花。@有时候一看就是一两个小时。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":1}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_36","textHome":"在学校受到了大家的关照，真的很感激。@不管什么时候都有人在我身边……@这就是万事靠朋友吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_37","textHome":"我想人的将来，总能靠自己的力量来改变。@只是如何改变，就取决于各人的选择了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_04","textHome":"这条街道，看起来到处都是病灶……"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_38","textHome":"花就会一直是花，不带任何邪念。而让这个@多彩世界投下阴影的，一直都是人类。@真是悲哀……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_39","textHome":"如果没有人制止魔女，这个世界就会@在悄然之间陷入混乱，更多人白白受苦。@我想要修正这种状况。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300500,"motion":0}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3005_00_40","textHome":"单对单必要的是「战术」。@集团对集团必要的是「战略」。@听起来很像，实际上差别很大。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":30050